Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:36.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}結果  幾度  壓抑自我情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不  那不過是掩飾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:42.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}其實早已崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}別來煩擾我  Craze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:50.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}堅持自我  即使四面楚歌  yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:53.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}身處起點時就已危機四伏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}全力出擊  Craze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}拿出所有本能  本性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:02.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}發起反攻  yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}倒在血影中的你  究竟是誰?
